Invoke these example dish scripts:

as command line script files.

    Example:
    	unix% dish circle -fg blue


as source'able script files in an interactive dish session.

    Example:
        unix% dish -fg blue -bg white
        % source circle
        % source hello


as executable scripts.

    1)  Make the following line the first line of the script:
    	#! /your/full/path/for/dish

    2)  chmod +x <name of script file>

    Example:
    	unix% circle -fg blue
